snippet.title: CYBRLICH and the Death Cult of Labor (Trailer)
snippet.description:
CYBRLICH and the Death Cult of Labor: A first person shooter that takes aim at corporate culture, capitalism, shitty jobs, and skeletons. 

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3336070/CYBRLICH_and_the_Death_Cult_of_Labor/
